# MCP server distribution — built by `bun run build:mcp` from mcp-server/,
# chained into `bun run build` so each Vercel deploy ships a fresh ZIP.
# Tracking it in git would embed every snapshot's blob into .git forever.
public/wordz-mcp.zip

# Supabase CLI local cache — pooler URL, version info, project ref.
# Created by `supabase link`; per-machine state, never committed.
supabase/.temp/
